name: Faisal Ahmad
text:
Gagak Rimang adalah nama kuda perang Arya Penangsang.

Lha terus siapa Arya Penangsang? 🤔

Kajian akademis menulis Arya Penangsang adalah seorang raja yang terlibat dalam intrik tak bertepi dalam kemelut berdarah - darah perebutan kekuasaan di Kerajaan Demak / Pajang.

Ia sosok kontroversial, antagonis namun lugas, pemberani serta patriotik. Cucu pertama Raden Patah itu pernah mbalelo, memboikot menyetor upeti sebab menganggap Sultan Hadiwijaya alias Joko Tingkir tidak sah serta ilegal sebagai raja Pajang.

Arya Penangsang naik takhta sebagai Sultan Demak V usai utusannya, Rangkud, berhasil menghabisi nyawa Raden Prawoto. Bloody mission itu dibakar oleh dendam kesumat lantaran Raden Prawoto adalah pembunuh Pangeran Surowiyoto, ayah Arya Penangsang.

Sewaktu berkuasa, Arya Penangsang memindahkan ibukota kerajaan dari Prawoto (Pati) ke Jipang Panolan (Cepu). Selain sebagai pusat pemerintahan, kotaraja juga difungsikan bandar perdagangan memanfaatkan posisi geografis di pinggir Bengawan Solo.

Pada akhirnya, santri kinasih Sunan Kudus itu tewas secara tragis, terhunus oleh kerisnya sendiri, Kyai Setan Kober, saat berduel sengit di atas kuda melawan Danang Sutawijaya, anak angkat Sultan Hadiwijaya. Senjata makan tuan, pengibaratannya.

Kini yang terlacak dari 'ruh perjuangan' Arya Penangsang adalah makam Gedong Ageng dan Santri Sembilan serta beberapa petilasan Kadipaten Jipang Panolan.

Terletak di Desa Jipang, kawasan ini disakralkan dan disucikan oleh warga. Pengunjung harus menjaga lisan, adab serta tata krama sewaktu berziarah, pamali untuk mengambil sekecil apapun benda dari tempat keramat ini.

Bagi penduduk setempat, Arya Penangsang adalah ksatria yang dihitamkan oleh sejarah..
textTranslated:
Gagak Rimang is the name of the Aryan Penangsang war horse.

Who is Arya Penangsang? 🤔

Academic studies write that Arya Penangsang is a king who is involved in endless intrigues in the bloody turmoil of the power struggle in the Kingdom of Demak / Pajang.

He is a controversial figure, antagonistic but straightforward, brave and patriotic. The first grandson of Raden Patah was once mbelo, boycotting paying tribute because he considered Sultan Hadiwijaya alias Joko Tingkir to be invalid and illegal as the king of Pajang.

Arya Penangsang ascended the throne as Sultan Demak V after his emissary, Rangkud, succeeded in killing Raden Prawoto. The bloody mission was burned by dark revenge because Raden Prawoto was the murderer of Prince Surowiyoto, Arya Penangsang's father.

When in power, Arya Penangsang moved the kingdom's capital from Prawoto (Pati) to Jipang Panolan (Cepu). In addition to being the center of government, the city also functions as a trading city taking advantage of its geographical position on the edge of Bengawan Solo.

In the end, the beloved student of Sunan Kudus died tragically, stabbed by his own dagger, Kyai Setan Kober, during a fierce duel on horseback against Danang Sutawijaya, the adopted son of Sultan Hadiwijaya. The master's weapon, the simile.

Now the traces of Arya Penangsang's 'struggle spirit' are the tombs of Gedong Ageng and Santri Sembilan as well as several tombs of the Jipang Panolan Duchy.

Located in Jipang Village, this area is sacred and purified by the people. Visitors must take care of language, manners and manners during pilgrimage, not to take even the smallest thing from this sacred place.

For the locals, Arya Penangsang is a knight blackened by history..

Sementara Arya Penangsang adalah adipati Jipang Panolan. Arya Penangsang merupakan sosok kontroversial dan pemberani. Ia menolak membayar pajak pada kerajaan Pajang karena menganggap Sultan Hadiwijaya tidak sah sebagai raja. Keputusan Arya Penangsang yang tidak mau membayar pajak tersebut akhirnya memuncak dan terjadilah perang antara Kerajaan Pajang dengan Kadipaten Jipang.
textTranslated:
Mentioning the name Arya Penangsang cannot be separated from the history of the Pajang kingdom, which at that time was led by Jaka Tingkir/Mas Karebet who had the title Sultan Hadiwijaya.
Meanwhile, Arya Penangsang is the duke of Jipang Panolan. Arya Penangsang is a controversial and brave figure. He refused to pay taxes to the Pajang kingdom because he considered Sultan Hadiwijaya illegitimate as king. Arya Penangsang's decision not to pay the tax finally culminated in a war between the Pajang Kingdom and the Jipang Duchy.

name: Taqiyya
text:
Salah satu maqom Waliyulloh yang berjuang bersama Syeh Jafar Sodiq atau biasa disebut Sunan Kudus . Terletak diperbatasan antata dua desa yaitu desa Sunggingan dan Demangan .
Tempatnya bersih , tenang dan tempat parkir luas , akses ziarah dibuka 24 jam ..
Hanya untuk akses masuk ke dalam kamar Kyai Telingsing terbatas , dibuka untuk umum pada saat hari Kamis malam atau Malam Jumat mulai pukul 4 sore hingga Jumat siang hari .. selain hari itu bisa menghubungi juru kunci Maqom untuk masuk ke dalam ..
Toiletnya bersih, Tempat wudu juga bersih..
Terbatas hanya ada 1 toilet , jadi harap bergantian dan menunggu apabila sedang ramai . Untuk akses kesini mudah diakses menggunakan motor, apabila menggunakan mobil harap berhati2 karena aksesnya lumayan sempit walaupum tidak terlalu sempit jadi masi bs d akses menggunakan mobil .
Silahkan bagi uang ingin berziarah kesini, dan tolong jaga kebersihan .
textTranslated:
One of the Waliyulloh maqom who fought alongside Syeh Jafar Sodiq or usually called Sunan Kudus. Located on the border between two villages, namely Sunggingan and Demangan villages.
The place is clean, quiet and has a large parking area, pilgrimage access is open 24 hours..
Only access to Kyai Telingsing's room is limited, it is open to the public on Thursday evenings or Friday nights from 4 pm to Friday afternoon... apart from that day, you can contact the Maqom caretaker to enter...
The toilets are clean, the ablution area is also clean...
There is limited to only 1 toilet, so please take turns and wait if it is busy. Access here is easy to access by motorbike. If you use a car, please be careful because the access is quite narrow, although not too narrow, so you can still access it by car.
Please share money to make a pilgrimage here, and please keep it clean.
title: Makam Mbah Kyai Telingsing

address: 5RQM+RHP, Sunggingan, Kota Kudus, Kudus Regency, Central Java 59317, Indonesia
name: Kana Taqiyya
text:
Salah satu waliyulloh di tanah kudus .
Yang berjuang bersama dengan Syekh Jafar Shodiq yang bergelar Kanjeng Sunan Kudus dalam masa syiar penyebaran Agama Islam di Tanah Jawa khususnya di Kudus .
Terletak di perbatasan antara desa Sunggingan dan Demangan . Tempatnya bersih dan parkiran luas buka 24 Jam tempatnya damai tenang dan nyaman untuk berdoa dan berziarah jadi lebih khusyuk . Motor dan mobil biaa masuk kedalam hanya saja akses untuk masuk mobil agak sempit jadi harap berhati2 bila masuk apalagi ketika berpapasan dgn kendaraan  lain .
Apabila ingin masuk lgsg ke Maqom Kyai Telingsing silahkan datang ketika malam Jumat, karena maqom yg di dalam tempat Kyai Telingsing dibuka mulai hari Kamis Sore jam 5 hingga jumat sore hari jam 5 . Selain hari itu pada hari2 biasa tetap masi bisa masuk ke areal makam tetapi tidak bisa masuk lgsg berdekatan dengan Makam Kyai Telingsing .
Silahkan berkunjung dan berziarah dan tolong jagalah kebersihan .
textTranslated:
One of the waliyulloh in the holy land.
Who fought together with Sheikh Jafar Shodiq who had the title Kanjeng Sunan Kudus during the period of spreading the spread of Islam in Java, especially in Kudus.
Located on the border between the villages of Sunggingan and Demangan. The place is clean and has a large parking area, open 24 hours. The place is peaceful, calm and comfortable for praying and making pilgrimages to make it more solemn. It is normal for motorbikes and cars to enter, but the access to enter the car is quite narrow, so please be careful when entering, especially when passing other vehicles.
If you want to go directly to the Kyai Telingsing Maqom, please come on Friday evening, because the maqom inside the Telingsing Kyai is open from Thursday afternoon at 5 until Friday afternoon at 5. Apart from that, on normal days you can still enter the tomb area but you cannot enter directly near the Kyai Telingsing tomb.
Please visit and make a pilgrimage and please maintain cleanliness.
title: Makam Mbah Kyai Telingsing

address: 5RQM+RHP, Sunggingan, Kota Kudus, Kudus Regency, Central Java 59317, Indonesia

text: Kiyai Telingsing merupakan salah satu tokoh penyebar agama islam di Kudus. Lokasinya tepat dibelakang Masjid Ciptomulyo Pengging, atau sebelah barat alun-alun Pengging, kalau kesini dimalam Jum'at Pahing akan sangat ramai seperti ada pasar malamnya.
textTranslated:
One of the biggest tombs in Pengging, the place where fathers, grandfathers, grandmothers and many of their siblings are buried, this tomb is not scary, far from being haunted because it is always busy, especially on Friday nights, there are usually lots of people making pilgrimages here. .
The location is right behind the Ciptomulyo Pengging Mosque, or west of Pengging square. If you come here on a Friday night, Pahing will be very busy, like there is a night market.

text:
Pernah mendengar cerita, bahwa sayyid abdurrohman mengikuti sayembara yang diadakan oleh bupati lasem, yang mana sayembara itu intinya siapa saja yang mampu menaklukkan penjajah pada area lasem, akan dihadiahi separuh dari wilayah lasem, kemudian beliau mengikutinya dan berhasil.

Setiap momen hari raya, sering melewati jalur dekat sini, namun baru sempat kali ini sejenak berziarah ke makam mbah sambu
textTranslated:
I once heard the story that Sayyid Abdurrohman took part in a competition held by the regent of Lasem, where the competition basically meant that whoever was able to conquer the invaders in the Lasem area, would be rewarded with half of the Lasem area, then he took part in it and succeeded.

Every time during the holidays, I often pass the route near here, but this is the first time I have had the opportunity to make a short pilgrimage to Mbah Sambu's grave.
title: Mbah Sambu (Sayyid Abdurrahman)

name: Ahmad Fahimi
text: Sayyid Abdurrahman Basyaiban atau yang lebih dikenal dengan Eyang Sambu bisa dikatakan sesepuh leluhur para ulama dan tokoh agama Islam di wilayah kecamatan Lasem,  dari beliulah lahir ulama ulama besar seperti mbah Baidowi, mbah Mansur, mbah Maksum, mbah aziz dan masih banyak lagi.  Terletak di belakang masjid Jami Lasem, membuat makam ini sangat recomended untuk diziarahi bagi para penikmat wisata religi. Jadi bila anda transit di masjid lasem, sangat rugi jika tidak sekalian berziarah di kompleks makam mbah sambu lasem.
textTranslated: Sayyid Abdurrahman Basyaiban or better known as Eyang Sambu can be said to be the ancestor of Islamic scholars and religious figures in the Lasem sub-district area, from him great scholars were born such as Mbah Baidowi, Mbah Mansur, Mbah Maksum, Mbah Aziz and many more.  Located behind the Jami Lasem mosque, this tomb is highly recommended as a pilgrimage for those who enjoy religious tourism. So, if you are transiting to the Lasem Mosque, it will be a loss if you don't also make a pilgrimage to the Mbah Sambu Lasem grave complex.
title: Mbah Sambu (Sayyid Abdurrahman)
